dcterms:description: Stanford Question Answering Dataset (SQuAD) is a reading comprehension dataset, consisting of 100,000+ question-answer pairs on 500+ articles. It has led to many research papers and significant breakthroughs in building effective reading comprehension systems.
dcterms:title: Stanford Question Answering Dataset (SQuAD)

dcterms:description: GloVe is a pre-trained word embedding model that is trained on 6 billion words from Wikipedia and Gigaword, providing word vectors that capture semantic meanings.
dcterms:title: GloVe (Global Vectors for Word Representation)
